### [Psalms Chapter 121](../../../bib/kjv/psa121.htm#001.md)

[Psalms 121:1](../../../bib/kjv/psa121.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_001">psa 121:1</span></span>

Hills - To Sion and Moriah, which are called the holy mountains.

[Psalms 121:5](../../../bib/kjv/psa121.htm#005.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_005">psa 121:5</span></span>

Shade - To keep thee from the burning heat of the sun.

[Psalms 121:6](../../../bib/kjv/psa121.htm#006.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_006">psa 121:6</span></span>

Smite - With excessive heat. Moon - With that cold and moisture which
come into the air by it. Intemperate heats and colds are the springs of
many diseases.

